# Reown Project Structure

Vue 3 + TypeScript Web3 app with Reown AppKit and NFT marketplace.

## Key Files
- [src/App.vue](mdc:src/App.vue) - AppKit setup
- [src/config/index.ts](mdc:src/config/index.ts) - Networks & adapters
- [src/composables/useNFTBuy.ts](mdc:src/composables/useNFTBuy.ts) - NFT purchase logic

## Required Environment Variables
- `VITE_PROJECT_ID` - Reown project ID
- `VITE_OPENSEA_API_KEY` - OpenSea API key

## Patterns
- Use `<script setup>` with Composition API
- Business logic in composables
- Reactive state with `ref()` and `reactive()`
